The paper deals with news recommendation, which is a subfield of information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of social information to enhance news rankings suggests that the paper may also belong to the subcategories of social networks (cs.SOC) and social media (cs.SI). The paper also mentions the use of natural language processing techniques (cs.CL) and resampling strategies, which are commonly used in machine learning (cs.DL).
